{"tid":815122,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"2021年歐聯或移師紐約","createTime":"2018-09-11T18:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T01:44:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"15fcf32428943f91e0d8559224cba37b222cb93c","tid":815122,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T18:45:16.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=C0cUpajQUBCSk6CEX00DVIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=29129d7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】美國市場龐大，繼西甲即將把數場比賽搬到美國，就連歐聯決賽也有機會移師美國。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙傳媒巨頭Imagina旗下公司Mediapro的CEO羅利斯（Jaume Roures）透露，正接洽把歐聯決賽搬到美國舉行的可能性：「我們正商討能夠在紐約主辦歐聯決賽。」由於未來2屆的歐聯決賽，已定於馬德里、伊斯坦堡舉行，因此最快也要2021年成事。<br />\n<br />\n若成事，在2021年將會是歐洲球壇有重大改變的一年，因為歐洲足協（UEFA）密謀將在2021/22球季，推出名字未定的第3項盃賽，令參賽總數達到96隊，目前正等待行政委員會通過，意味着歐洲3大盃賽的時代重臨。<br />\n<br />\n史上首場在美國舉行的西甲，很大機會在下年1月27日上演。雖然球員不太支持，但羅利斯認為成事機會非常樂觀：「我們正在商討，基羅納很有興趣，他們上季才升至頂級聯賽，但在15天已成為全世界的焦點，此舉同時可提升西甲的形象。」"},{"pid":"8719b6dac922ddf46f11fb54bbced1ace237f021","tid":815122,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T18:45:50.000Z","msg":"趕盡禾地藍波撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad68892f64baaa84de35f8b377209b482fd9cee","tid":815122,"uid":130060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T18:53:34.000Z","msg":"正呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b14ecd4a38b5cc65ac40524256f7068843a3337","tid":815122,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T18:54:26.000Z","msg":"足波撚笑到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9f87688bc5a10958883659cb39e7f5c32